§ THE TIERS (free vs premium · cosmetic-channel-only)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ FREE-TIER (always-available · gift-economy)
  ⊑ browse aggregate-multiversal-events @ low-resolution-summary · cohort-statistics
  ⊑ browse opt-in-public-imprints from-other-players · text-summary
  ⊑ imprint your-own-deeds at BASIC-fidelity (event-class + date + brief-summary)
  ⊑ search by tag · biome · element · class
  ⊑ view personal-history-imprints (your-own-deeds always-readable to-yourself · 100% fidelity LOCAL)
  ⊑ Memorial-Wall in-public-Homes (per spec/16) is-FREE for-visitors
  ⊑ Stabilized-Essence-purchases of legacy-Bazaar items are-imprint-events FREE-tier

§ PREMIUM-TIER (Aetheric-Shards · cosmetic-channel · per spec/13)
  ⊑ HIGH-FIDELITY-IMPRINT : 16-band-spectral-rendered scene-snapshot · audio-loop · BLAKE3-content-hash · permanent
    cost : 50-200 Aetheric-Shards per-imprint · scales-with-fidelity
  ⊑ AKASHIC-SHRINE-DECORATIONS : 7+ shrine-styles · 30+ rune-kits · 16 ambient-particle-FX · cssl-fractal-amp variants
    cost : 100-500 Aetheric-Shards per-cosmetic · or via gacha-pull (per spec/13)
  ⊑ ETERNAL-ATTRIBUTION : permanent-author-credit on-public-imprints · displayed-with player-handle · rare-aura-glyph
    cost : 1000 Aetheric-Shards per-deed · ONE-TIME-PERMANENT
  ⊑ HISTORICAL-RECONSTRUCTIONS : visit-procgen-recreation of past-cohort-events · museum-tour-mode · cssl-render-v2 historical-reconstruction
    cost : 50 Aetheric-Shards per-tour · 30-min-time-limit per-tour · cosmetic-only
  ⊑ COMMISSIONED-IMPRINTS : pay-to-have GM narrate your-deed in-Akashic-flavor-text · cssl-host-gm consumes-this · permanent
    cost : 200-500 Aetheric-Shards · uses GM-host-LLM-token-budget (margin built-in)
  ⊑ BOOSTED-MEMORIAL-WALL : your-Home-Memorial-Wall has-3× capacity for-visitor-spore-ascriptions · cosmetic-only
    cost : 300 Aetheric-Shards · 6-month-duration

§ EXPLICIT-NON-PAYWALLED @ NEVER monetize-these (gameplay-advantage)
  ⊑ Coherence-Score-eval ← deterministic · same-state same-score
  ⊑ Ascension threshold ← public-known · same-rules-everyone
  ⊑ Bazaar-listing capacity ← per spec/13 5-tier · earned-via-NG+
  ⊑ Stabilized-Essence-balance ← earned-only
  ⊑ gear-stats / Coherence-axes ← gameplay-not-monetization
  ⊑ KAN-canary-class ← deterministic · NOT-purchasable
  ⊑ NPC-cocreative-bias ← player's-LOCAL-θ · NOT-affected by-Aetheric-spend

§ payment-flow-from-spec/13-monetization (Stripe-tier-skip + gacha + direct-purchase)
  ⊑ Aetheric-Shards purchase → Stripe-checkout @ cssl-edge `/api/payments/stripe/checkout` (per spec/13)
  ⊑ shards-balance @ cssl-supabase 0022_payments aetheric_shard_balances table
  ⊑ shards-spent on-Akashic-features → cssl-supabase 0023+ akashic_imprints + cosmetic_purchases
  ⊑ NEW migration 0037_akashic_records.sql : akashic_imprints + akashic_shrine_cosmetics + akashic_attributions
  ⊑ NEW migration 0038_akashic_rls.sql : RLS player-scoped · public-read for-published-imprints

