§ TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE (consume substrate · NO new shadow-systems)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ Akashic-Records LIVES-ON Σ-Chain TIER-3 multiversal-stream
  ⊑ each-imprint = a-Σ-Chain-event with kind="akashic.imprint" + payload-shape
  ⊑ Ed25519-signed by-player's-sovereign-key (anonymizable per spec/14 P1-tier)
  ⊑ BLAKE3-merkle-rooted on-canonical-state @ event-tick
  ⊑ verifiable-Coherence-Proof per spec/14 § COHERENCE-PROOF

§ asset-data
  ⊑ HIGH-FIDELITY-IMPRINT : cssl-host-asset-bundle LAB-v1 with-scene-snapshot + audio-loop + BLAKE3-content-hash
  ⊑ stored @ Supabase Storage (LAB-binary-blobs · CDN-delivered) · player pays-shards · server-stores
  ⊑ public-imprints CDN-cached · accessible-by-attribution-link · permanent

§ shrine-decorations
  ⊑ cssl-host-asset-bundle LAB-v1 cosmetic-only-flag · per spec/13 monetization-axiom
  ⊑ per-Home cssl-host-home-dimension stores-equipped-cosmetic-IDs · references-server-entitlement-DB
  ⊑ server-validates entitlement on-equip-action

§ historical-reconstructions
  ⊑ cssl-host-procgen-rooms + cssl-host-fab-procgen + cssl-host-causal-seed combine-to recreate-past-cohort-events
  ⊑ deterministic-recompute @ given seed + event-payload + Coherence-Proof verifies-match
  ⊑ cssl-render-v2 + cssl-spectral-render + cssl-fractal-amp render the-tour
  ⊑ time-limited-tours via cssl-host-config TTL · server-token expires-after-tour

§ commissioned-imprints
  ⊑ cssl-host-gm narrates @ commission-request · narrative-text generated-once · stored-permanent
  ⊑ GM-host runs-LLM-via cssl-edge companion-proxy (per spec/13) · margin-built-in-to-shards-cost
  ⊑ player can-iterate (3 free-iterations) before-commit · once-committed permanent

