  CRATE-B22 NEW `cssl-host-akashic-records` ← imprint state-machine · fidelity-tier · attribution-permanence · ≥ 32 tests · 1500 LOC max
  CRATE-B23 NEW `cssl-host-akashic-shrine`  ← shrine cosmetic-state · 7+ archetypes · placement-via Home-dimension · ≥ 22 tests · 1200 LOC max
